# Note: firebase-config.js IS committed to this repo on purpose.
# Firebase web SDK config values (apiKey, projectId, etc.) are PUBLIC by design —
# they ship to every visitor's browser anyway. Security is enforced server-side
# via Firestore rules, not by hiding the file.

